{{Top|leg}}
The '''Dual Cannon''' was a weapon installed in the [[Arakyd Industries/Legends|Arakyd Industries]] [[Security droid/Legends|security droid]] [[Z-58-0|Zeeo]]. It fired large waves of energy and was capable of killing multiple enemies, consuming large amounts of Zeeo's energy in the process.
[[File:Dualcannonzeeo.jpg|thumb|right|Rianna Saren uses the dual cannon]]

{{Weapon-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The Dual Cannon appears in the [[Wikipedia:Nintendo DS|Nintendo DS]] version of the game ''[[Star Wars: Lethal Alliance]]''. To use it, players must first achieve the ''Maximum Alliance'' status by using Zeeo to help Rianna defeat her foes.

